Is anyone having trouble with the groupby filter?  The .grouper is returning an object all of the sudden.

I found the problem - .grouper was returning an object because it was a multi-select.  Previous dev was using regex replace to strip out some content.  It does seem that HubSpot may have added another field to the object, label="null".  As a result, the regex replace was returning the wrong content.
